views.ui_expr:
#"SYSTEM_SYSRULES_recordGridField"(
  columns: {
    #"SYSTEM_SYSRULES_gridColumn"(
      label: "Username",
      sortField: recordType!AS_GSS_User_RECORD.username,
      value: fv!row[recordType!AS_GSS_User_RECORD.username]
    ),
    #"SYSTEM_SYSRULES_gridColumn"(
      label: "First Name",
      sortField: recordType!AS_GSS_User_RECORD.firstName,
      value: #"SYSTEM_SYSRULES_linkField"(
        links: {
          #"SYSTEM_SYSRULES_recordLink"(
            label: fv!row[recordType!AS_GSS_User_RECORD.firstName],
            recordType: recordType!AS_GSS_User_RECORD,
            identifier: fv!identifier
          )
        }
      )
    ),
    #"SYSTEM_SYSRULES_gridColumn"(
      label: "Last Name",
      sortField: recordType!AS_GSS_User_RECORD.lastName,
      value: fv!row[recordType!AS_GSS_User_RECORD.lastName]
    ),
    #"SYSTEM_SYSRULES_gridColumn"(
      label: "Email",
      sortField: recordType!AS_GSS_User_RECORD.email,
      value: fv!row[recordType!AS_GSS_User_RECORD.email]
    ),
    #"SYSTEM_SYSRULES_gridColumn"(
      label: "Phone Number",
      sortField: recordType!AS_GSS_User_RECORD.phoneNumber,
      value: fv!row[recordType!AS_GSS_User_RECORD.phoneNumber]
    ),
    #"SYSTEM_SYSRULES_gridColumn"(
      label: "Created By",
      sortField: recordType!AS_GSS_User_RECORD.createdBy,
      value: fv!row[recordType!AS_GSS_User_RECORD.createdBy]
    ),
    #"SYSTEM_SYSRULES_gridColumn"(
      label: "Created Datetime",
      sortField: recordType!AS_GSS_User_RECORD.createdDatetime,
      value: if(
        isnull(
          fv!row[recordType!AS_GSS_User_RECORD.createdDatetime]
        ),
        fv!row[recordType!AS_GSS_User_RECORD.createdDatetime],
        datetext(
          fv!row[recordType!AS_GSS_User_RECORD.createdDatetime],
          "default"
        )
      ),
      align: "END"
    ),
    #"SYSTEM_SYSRULES_gridColumn"(
      label: "Modified By",
      sortField: recordType!AS_GSS_User_RECORD.modifiedBy,
      value: fv!row[recordType!AS_GSS_User_RECORD.modifiedBy]
    ),
    #"SYSTEM_SYSRULES_gridColumn"(
      label: "Modified Datetime",
      sortField: recordType!AS_GSS_User_RECORD.modifiedDatetime,
      value: if(
        isnull(
          fv!row[recordType!AS_GSS_User_RECORD.modifiedDatetime]
        ),
        fv!row[recordType!AS_GSS_User_RECORD.modifiedDatetime],
        datetext(
          fv!row[recordType!AS_GSS_User_RECORD.modifiedDatetime],
          "default"
        )
      ),
      align: "END"
    ),
    #"SYSTEM_SYSRULES_gridColumn"(
      label: "Is Active",
      sortField: recordType!AS_GSS_User_RECORD.isActive,
      value: fv!row[recordType!AS_GSS_User_RECORD.isActive]
    )
  },
  pageSize: cons!AS_CO_ENUM_PAGE_SIZE_LARGE,
  shadeAlternateRows: true
)

constants.name: AS_CO_ENUM_PAGE_SIZE_LARGE
constants.description: 50 - LARGE page size, used for grids and other paging situations
